


06-12-2023 Setting up Maven on local machine


1. Download Maven https://maven.apache.org/
2. Set up MAVE_HOME
	NOTE: Make sure JAVA_HOME is set

	MAC: 
	export JAVA_HOME=/Library/Java/JavaVirtualMachines/jdk1.8.0_361.jdk/Contents/Home
	export M2_HOME=/Applications/apache-maven-3.9.2
	export PATH=$PATH:$M2_HOME/bin

	Check your terminal if it is
	zsh 	-> touch .zshrc	
	bash	-> touch .bash_profile


	WINDOWS:
	MAVEN_HOME=path
	M2_HOME=path

3. Run mvn --version and make sure it is installed



HOW TO RUN Suites from our Terminal or Command Prompt
-Open a terminal or cmd
-Navigate to your repo
-Make sure you see pom.xml as a file in the directory
-Run your command 
	mvn test -PSmoke



HOW TO RUN Suites on IntelliJ IDEA Terminal
-Go to your project on IntelliJ IDEA
-Open IntelliJ IDEA Terminal
-Run your command 
	mvn test -PSmoke














